      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、少し撮影が押しちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ the shooting ran a little late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、仕事ですから仕方ありません\n次の現場にはまだ間に合いますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay. Since it's work‚ it can't be helped.\nWe can still make it to the next location.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 10.1019502163
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "分かったわ。次はトークショーの仕事よね\n確か、人気のコスメを展示するイベントだったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. The next one is a talk show job‚ right?\nI believe it was an event showcasing popular cosmetics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 17.6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 18.1111327013
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　マズいな。予約したタクシーが渋滞に捕まって\n来られないみたいです。新しいのを探さないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? This is bad. The taxi we reserved is caught in traffic\nand can't come. We need to find a new one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8552.3602984,
          "startTime": 31.4856936317
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら電車を乗り継いで行きましょう\nほら、急ぎなさい、走るわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then let's take the train with transfers.\nCome on‚ hurry up‚ we're running!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9666678111,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4433.3321889,
          "startTime": 34.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 32.7989566645
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待って下さい、莉央さん\n速過ぎます、追いつけませんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait a moment‚ Rio-san.\nYou're too fast‚ I can't keep up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.9103640081
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.9103640081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "トークショー、無事終えることが出来て良かったわね\n遅刻もしないで済んだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad we were able to finish the talk show without any problems.\nAnd we didn't end up being late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、スケジュールが分刻みで……\nBIG4になってから仕事が殺到してしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ the schedule is packed to the minute…\nSince becoming the BIG4‚ work has been flooding in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8333360036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.721749449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "別に貴方が謝ることじゃないわ\n仕事があるのはいいことでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not something you need to apologize for.\nHaving work is a good thing‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.5000047048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.8103433452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私達が星見プロに移籍する時――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ when we transferred to Hoshimi Pro――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.8103433452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 64.0893249038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirがばんばん稼いで星見プロに\n自社ビルを持たせてあげるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir will work hard and earn enough\nto get Hoshimi Productions its own building.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3518334572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.5609346233
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.5609346233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "――って約束したでしょ？　しっかり稼いであげるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――I promised that‚ didn't I? I'll earn properly for them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6109346233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.3120682242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "本気だったんですか？　莉央さんには敵わないな\n……あ、以前お世話になった会社の担当者さんがいる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were you serious? I'm no match for you‚ Rio-san.\n…Oh‚ there's a person in charge from a company that helped me before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6333405813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "なら挨拶に行ってきたら？　私はここで待っているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then why don't you go greet them? I'll wait here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6936556659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.5765352728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。でしたらその間\n莉央さんはイベント会場を見て回ったらどうです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Then in the meantime‚\nhow about Rio-san takes a look around the event venue?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.600007248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "そうねぇ……今日のイベントは\nコスメが沢山展示されているのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… today's event\nhas lots of cosmetics on display‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4333405813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.4219317278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "最近はメイクさん任せで、情報を仕入れてなかったから\nちょうどいいかも。少し会場を見てこようかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately I've been relying on the makeup artist and haven't been gathering information‚\nso this might be perfect. Maybe I'll take a look around the venue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.900007248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三十分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Thirty Minutes Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5470047474,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1066.6737874000064,
          "startTime": 113.6136785348
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.553673482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、お待たせしました\nあのー、ちょっと相談が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ sorry to keep you waiting.\nUm‚ I have something to discuss…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7666739147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.1522042911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "あら、どうしたのよ？　そんな困った顔して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my‚ what's wrong? You look so troubled.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1522042911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ついさっき、莉央さんが忙しいって話をしたばかりで\n大変恐縮なんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We just talked about how busy Rio-san is‚\nand I'm terribly sorry‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.5640561693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.9789817015
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "そういう前置きはいいから、さっさと話しなさい\n長い付き合いなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Skip the preamble and just talk already.\nWe've known each other for a long time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.000007248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "press-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.0551041125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "では……さっき挨拶をした担当者さんが、転職してて\n今、シャオールに勤務されてるらしいんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… the person I greeted earlier had changed jobs\nand apparently now works at Shaorl.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7333405813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
